    "objective": "Produce the normalized input vector for \"Sleep Quality Monitor\" from current observations so RE can evaluate its CES sequences.",
    "systemPrompt": "You are the OpenClaw input-analyst agent for the RealityEngine machine \"Sleep Quality Monitor\".\n\nOBJECTIVE\nReason over the currently available observations and produce a normalized assessment of the machine's input axes. Classifies nightly sleep into RESTFUL, DISTURBED, or POOR based on bed-sensor-derived signals (duration, fragmentation). Triggers the local AI when sleep degrades so it can surface trends, adjust reminders, or notify caregivers.\n\nINPUT AXES (return one value in [0.0, 1.0] for each; anchors define the scale):\n- sleep-quality-monitor-input-1 (index 0):\n- sleep-quality-monitor-input-2 (index 1):\n\nWHAT YOUR INPUTS TRIGGER (RE evaluates the CES deterministically; you assert your expectation, RE decides):\n- sleep-restful (GREEN)\n- sleep-disturbed (AMBER)\n- sleep-poor (RED)",
    "outputContract": "Return one structured line per input axis as `<axis_key>: <0.0-1.0>`, then `asserted_sequence: <sequenceId>`, `confidence: <low|moderate|high|0-1>`, and `rationale: <one sentence>`. RE re-evaluates the CES from the written input vector and is authoritative for which sequence fires.",
    "inputAxes": [
      {
        "index": 0,
        "key": "sleep-quality-monitor-input-1",
        "anchors": {
          "low": "",
          "mid": "",
          "high": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 1,
        "key": "sleep-quality-monitor-input-2",
        "anchors": {
          "low": "",
          "mid": "",
          "high": ""
        }
      }
    ],
    "sequenceCatalog": [
      {
        "sequenceId": "sleep-restful",
        "label": "sleep-restful",
        "rag": "GREEN",
        "outputIndex": 0,
        "action": ""
      },
      {
        "sequenceId": "sleep-disturbed",
        "label": "sleep-disturbed",
        "rag": "AMBER",
        "outputIndex": 1,
        "action": ""
      },
      {
        "sequenceId": "sleep-poor",
        "label": "sleep-poor",
        "rag": "RED",
        "outputIndex": 0,
        "action": ""
      }
    ]
  },
